data.description: Beautiful ranch brick home in Englewood Hills! This home was completely remodeled in 2015 (windows, gutters, AC, furnace, flooring and more) and has been impeccably kept. There are 3 nice sized bedrooms and 2 full baths. With a large living room and family room, there is plenty of room to entertain.  The living room, dining room and hallway all have hardwood laminate flooring; the family room and bedrooms have luxurious carpet; and the kitchen, foyer and bathrooms have ceramic tile. Gas heat and central air. There is a 2 car garage, as well as plenty of parking in the driveway or on the quiet street. Outside, you can enjoy the view from the covered front porch or the new concrete patio out back. Other updates include a new privacy fence, new liner/crown on the fireplace, and a new hot water heater. New roof with a 50 year transferrable warranty is being installed mid-December. Immediate possession!
